data.description: OVER 4000 SF home with 6+ acres in the conveniently located in the city limits in a dead end street. 5 bedrooms and an office! The updated Kitchen and dining room are beautiful and welcoming! Above ground pool, fenced in back yard. Storage Building, garden space, some wooded property with mature trees. Fireplaces in the living rm and den. There are two full baths and a 1/2 bath on the main level and a third full bath is plumbed in the downstairs/basement just waiting on the finishes of your choice. There are TWO Laundry rooms one on each level! Space Space and more Space. Basement has an outside access with potential to be an additional living area or workshop. 4.6 miles to Nestle Purina! convenient to UNC-Rockingham hospital/medical facilities, restaurants, shopping, golf/swimming, skating, parks, rivers. Eden even has a Drive-In Movie Theater! Looking for a wonderful, welcoming small town? THIS IS HOME!
